data.name: lblToLowerRegex.ToolTip
data.value: MFM capitalizes the first letter of each word in a name by default, to make the item name easier to read. The Convert to Lower regular expression tells MFM which words in the name to convert to lower case. The convert to lower regular expression contains the articles between spaces “ “ separated by a vertical line “|”.
